text:
Ah...!
You did really well until the end, Tenka...!

Clearing the final stage...!
Got the reward...!

So, have you decided what to buy?
You mentioned consulting your parents.

Y-yeah...
They said no to anything big, so...

Might get a pillow and...
an eye mask...!

So... can Tenka send you the URL...
to buy them online, Producer-san?

Oh, sure.
I'll order them right away so they arrive soon.

Hehe... did it...!
Once I get home... gonna sleep a lot...!

All day long...
N-No, maybe... for a week...!

It's great that you'll rest, but...
make sure to come to work during that time too...!
